161
00:18:43,388 --> 00:18:45,788
I told her
appearances aren't everything.

162
00:18:45,990 --> 00:18:48,857
- Would you agree?
- I certainly would.

163
00:18:49,060 --> 00:18:53,326
Now, this new fellow, Nezmeroz.
Is that his name?

164
00:18:54,098 --> 00:18:56,259
Nemerov, sir.

165
