I give them a while to get used to it.

187
00:20:19,284 --> 00:20:21,514
Then I tell them.

188
00:20:21,719 --> 00:20:25,018
- I understand.
- Good.

189
00:20:25,223 --> 00:20:27,691
But I'm right about Nemerov.

190
00:20:29,994 --> 00:20:33,623
Your girlfriend like
this stubborn streak in you?

191
