00:23:55,800 --> 00:23:59,736
In fact, what I thought I'd found
was a garden ornament.

228
00:24:15,520 --> 00:24:17,044
Hello, Cathy?

229
00:24:17,255 --> 00:24:22,921
Hi. I'm glad you called. I'm running late.
