248
00:26:24,181 --> 00:26:27,776
Zdravstvuyte, William Cabot.

249
00:26:29,020 --> 00:26:30,578
President Nemerov.

250
00:26:44,201 --> 00:26:45,998
Pleasure, sir.

251
00:26:46,203 --> 00:26:48,398
May I present Mrs Lathrop.

252
00:26:48,606 --> 00:26:50,164
Mr President.

253
00:26:50,374 --> 00:26:53,172
- General Rand.
- Mr President.

254
00:26:53,377 --> 00:26:55,709
- Dr Ryan.
- Mr President.

255
00:27:00,918 --> 00:27:05,378
You must be the Dr Ryan who's done
