00:27:41,892 --> 00:27:47,455
Where you received
highest honors in English.

261
00:27:51,268 --> 00:27:52,826
I like you.

262
00:27:54,638 --> 00:27:57,334
Well, in that case, so do I.

263
00:28:00,444 --> 00:28:04,175
I apologize for interjecting myself
