278
00:28:52,663 --> 00:28:54,722
It is none of your concern.

279
00:28:56,801 --> 00:28:59,429
Stability is our concern.

280
00:28:59,637 --> 00:29:02,731
Peace in Chechnya is our concern.

281
00:29:03,474 --> 00:29:06,534
And, if I may speak frankly...

282
00:29:07,578 --> 00:29:10,706
...your control over your military
concerns us too.

283
00:29:18,522 --> 00:29:24,791
For you to get involved here, it's... like
sleeping with another man's wife.

284
00:29:26,430 --> 00:29:29,490
And what you are suggesting
is that afterward

285
00:29:29,700 --> 00:29:32,931
they can all live together
under the same roof.

286
00:29:34,772 --> 00:29:40,142
But what really happens is
the betrayed husband buys a gun.

287
00:29:49,653 --> 00:29:52,918
- That went well.
- Who's the guy with Nemerov?

288
00:29:53,123 --> 00:29:55,683
- Anatoli Grushkov.
- Old KGB?

289
00:29:55,893 --> 00:30:01,024
He's been around since Brezhnev.
Nobody's had the guts to get rid of him.

290
00:30:01,232 --> 00:30:03,200
Because he knows
