292
00:30:20,351 --> 00:30:24,811
And we were able to obtain a roster
of their scientists at Arzamas.

293
00:30:25,022 --> 00:30:27,786
Who's who, what their expertise is.

294
00:31:01,091 --> 00:31:02,718
Arzamas-1 6 is home

295
