318
00:33:49,460 --> 00:33:53,453
We touch down at Andrews at 21 30.
Tell him to meet me there.

319
00:33:53,664 --> 00:33:56,292
Sir? Those three missing scientists.

320
00:33:56,500 --> 00:33:58,695
Milinov's expertise is detonators.

321
00:33:58,902 --> 00:34:01,871
Spassky's expertise
