339
00:35:27,391 --> 00:35:29,723
I'll see you at the car.

340
00:35:41,138 --> 00:35:42,833
Still loving your desk job?

341
00:35:44,341 --> 00:35:46,866
Yeah, I am.

342
00:35:47,077 --> 00:35:49,409
How's your Russian?

343
00:35:49,613 --> 00:35:51,274
Still works. Why?

344
00:35:52,716 --> 00:35:57,176
Three Russian nuclear scientists are
missing. I need to know where they are.

345
00:36:02,226 --> 00:36:04,023
I wasn't doing this any more.

346
00:36:04,228 --> 00:36:06,958
I just need information this time,
Johnny.

347
00:36:07,164 --> 00:36:11,828
Your orders are on the plane.
Wheels up at 2330. Have a nice flight.

348
00:36:21,345 --> 00:36:26,146
Sunday night, 8.00, at the Hilton. The
tickets are in the name of John Clark.

349
00:36:26,750 --> 00:36:29,878
- You do have a tux?
- Yeah, yes, sir.

350
00:36:36,326 --> 00:36:41,821
My beautiful wife, Julie, is from
New Jersey. 1 5 electoral votes.

