355
00:37:02,953 --> 00:37:06,480
Maybe after dinner we can...

356
00:37:06,690 --> 00:37:09,056
...we can get a room here.

357
00:37:09,259 --> 00:37:11,489
I already did.

358
00:37:12,763 --> 00:37:15,357
- You didn't.
- Yes, I did.

359
00:37:16,733 --> 00:37:20,863
...I did, on a handful of occasions,
smoke marijuana.

360
00:37:22,406 --> 00:37:25,671
California, 54 electoral votes.

361
00:38:03,213 --> 00:38:07,513
At 0600 Moscow time, the Russians
launched a massive artillery strike

362
00:38:07,718 --> 00:38:10,915
against Grozny,
the capital of Chechnya.

363
00:38:11,121 --> 00:38:15,888
The shells contained an experimental
chemical weapon, a nerve agent.

364
00:38:16,093 --> 00:38:19,790
Saturation, you can see
on the sat photos, took 20 minutes,

365
00:38:19,997 --> 00:38:23,524
after which every person
inside a radius of 1 2 miles

366
00:38:23,734 --> 00:38:28,603
was rendered helpless by symptoms
approximating late-stage cerebral palsy.

367
00:38:28,805 --> 00:38:31,330
- Oh, my God.
