419
00:42:56,840 --> 00:43:00,901
- Where is the package?
- It left Haifa a week ago.

420
00:43:02,579 --> 00:43:04,706
I'm told these things can kill you.

421
00:43:08,351 --> 00:43:11,650
But so much has changed.

422
00:43:13,056 --> 00:43:19,484
Perhaps the new situation suggests
we consider... a different approach?

423
00:43:22,966 --> 00:43:26,732
Maybe try to bring Russia
more into Europe,

424
00:43:26,936 --> 00:43:29,905
more into our way of thinking?

425
00:43:30,106 --> 00:43:33,439
We have discussed that,
Monsieur Monceau,

426
00:43:33,643 --> 00:43:36,771
and with your concurrence, rejected it.

427
00:43:36,980 --> 00:43:40,143
Oh. Perhaps we were hasty.

428
00:43:40,350 --> 00:43:43,478
- Perhaps our plan is...
- Is what?

429
00:43:48,124 --> 00:43:50,820
Not perfectly conceived.

430
00:43:53,229 --> 00:43:58,633
Are you crazy? All over
the world, right-wing parties,

431
00:43:58,835 --> 00:44:03,704
nationalist movements,
Nazis, Aryan Nations,

432
00:44:03,907 --> 00:44:07,035
all working together for the first time.

433
00:44:07,243 --> 00:44:09,040
Is that not perfect?

434
00:44:16,686 --> 00:44:21,646
Well, I respect the will and judgment
of my friends.

435
00:44:22,459 --> 00:44:26,486
But in light of the week's events,
I am grown...

436
00:44:27,731 --> 00:44:30,632
...uncomfortable with this plan.

437
00:44:30,834 --> 00:44:34,361
So I must... beg your leave.

438
00:44:40,410 --> 00:44:42,071
Gentlemen.

439
00:44:47,250 --> 00:44:49,775
Herr Haft will help you out.

440
00:44:55,392 --> 00:44:56,950
Your scarf, monsieur.

441
00:45:13,143 --> 00:45:16,442
Watch it with that thing.
