444
00:45:57,654 --> 00:45:58,951
The navy.

445
00:45:59,155 --> 00:46:01,589
The navy? I was in the navy.

446
00:46:02,592 --> 00:46:06,028
Hospital ship, six years. You?

447
00:46:09,399 --> 00:46:10,696
Eight months.

448
00:46:11,768 --> 00:46:13,668
Oh. You wash out?

449
00:46:21,544 --> 00:46:23,808
All right, brother.
You have a good one.

450
00:46:27,050 --> 00:46:28,950
Yeah, brother.

451
00:46:36,192 --> 00:46:41,425
...not realizing the rest of the world is
watching and will take a cue from us...

