00:46:41,631 --> 00:46:45,123
The unprecedented attack
on Chechnya

453
00:46:45,335 --> 00:46:49,237
signals a dangerous
and troubling shift in Russian policy.

454
00:46:49,439 --> 00:46:54,206
It demands the toughest and most
unambiguous response from the West.

455
00:46:55,078 --> 00:47:00,175
NATO forces are on their way to
Chechnya to serve as peacekeepers

456
00:47:00,383 --> 00:47:06,219
and to provide humanitarian aid
to victims of this monstrous...

457
00:47:09,292 --> 00:47:11,419
I expected this.

458
00:47:11,628 --> 00:47:13,323
Really?

459
00:47:18,968 --> 00:47:20,401
What will you do?

460
00:47:20,603 --> 00:47:22,833
Nothing.

461
00:47:23,039 --> 00:47:26,770
We will do nothing.

462
00:47:28,645 --> 00:47:33,105
These are four hours old. Russian
12th, 15th and 2nd tank regiments.

