465
00:47:38,988 --> 00:47:44,255
Jack, Nemerov's got, like, 1 9,000
tanks. No way NATO can match that.

466
00:47:44,460 --> 00:47:46,792
That's why he's not gonna move them.

467
00:47:46,996 --> 00:47:50,989
It's like chess.
